  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: TCM Services</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Therapist</strong></li><li>Working Location: Orchard (Walk distance from MRT)</li><li>Working Hours: 6 Days per week (Weekdays 10am – 8pm/ Weekend 9am – 5pm)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic Salary up to $3000 + Commission + Performance Bonus</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Provide body massage services tailored to each customer’s needs.</li><li>Ensure a professional and empathetic interaction with customers throughout each therapy session.</li><li>Maintain a clean and calm treatment environment, ensuring customer comfort.</li><li>Advise on post-treatment care and recommend suitable follow-up sessions.</li><li>Record all treatment details accurately.</li><li>Other duties as assigned.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum ITE certification in a related discipline.</li><li>Prior experience in massage therapy preferred (training will be provided for candidates without experience).</li><li>Capable to commit work during weekends.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#78003 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Rachael Lee | EA Reg No.: R2093131</p>",
